 able to sense and cooperate with the intention of these forces to promote healing in the patient.\r\n\r\nTo treat the practitioner uses their traditional postural assessment in conjunction with an  assessment of the whole being using the inner life rhythms as a diagnostic tool which is achieved by gently places their hands on your body.Â  This enables the practitioner to assess the inner health and function of all organs and tissues of the body and also to gain an understanding of how other levels of being (energetic, emotional, mental and spiritual) are influencing the health and wellbeing of the individual assessed.\r\n\r\nTogether with traditional methods of treatment such as manipulation, articulation and soft tissue therapy (which can still be used where appropriate), biodynamic Osteopathy helps to enhance long term health in patients with a wider variety of health issues.\r\n\r\nFor more information on this type of therapy, please call and speak to one of our Osteopaths.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/practitioners/shari\">Dr Shari Trimble</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/practitioners/paul\">Dr Paul Turner</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Biodynamic/Craniosacral Osteopathy','','publish','open','open','','biodynamic-cranial-osteopathy','','','2010-10-10 13:43:59','2010-10-10 03:43:59','',32,'http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.com/?page_id=28',1,'page','',0),(29,1,'2009-09-28 20:02:16','2009-09-29 03:02:16','','Biodynamic/Cranial Osteopathy','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision','','','2009-09-28 20:02:16','2009-09-29 03:02:16','',28,'http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.com/?p=29',0,'revision','',0),(30,1,'2009-09-28 20:02:39','2009-09-29 03:02:39','gffdhfhg','Biodynamic/Cranial Osteopathy','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-2','','','2009-09-28 20:02:39','2009-09-29 03:02:39','',28,'http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.com/?p=30',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2010-10-10 10:54:22','2010-10-10 00:54:22','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-166\" src=\"http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.co